## Issue description

Build failure with Boost 1.53 and current git master related to usage of boost::variant.  It's not necessarily a pybind11 problem for fixing, but may be something to document regarding minimum requirements.  Or it may be that the usage of variant could be tweaked to avoid the problem.  The forward declaration might be indicative of a missing include (or it might be that this version of boost is buggy).

Boost 1.53 is the version provided by RHEL/CentOS 7.

